description: What’s Happening? At Knight Connections, you’ll take part in exciting activities that make meeting new people easy and stress-free:✅ Speed Matching – Quick, fun conversations to help you find compatibility.🌸 LEGO Flower Exchange – Build a flower and gift it to a potential roommate.🧸 Stuff-a-Plush Station – Create a heart-shaped pillow to keep or share.🎲 Human Bingo – Break the ice while mingling and learning about others.📌 Connections Wall – Share fun facts about yourself and discover common ground.🏡 Housing Operations Table – Get answers to all your housing selection questions.💬 Feedback Station – Share your thoughts and enter a raffle for prizes!   Why Should You Attend? 💡 Meet potential roommates in a low-pressure, fun environment.🏡 Learn about housing options and find the right fit for you.🎁 Win prizes, enjoy Valentine’s-themed activities, and make new friends!
